comments: Had this teacher back in 2001 for Eastern Philosophy (I think that is what it was called). Back then I was working towards my Associates. Now I\'m working on my Masters and still use the concepts learned from this class in my personal and professional lives. Understanding other cultures belief systems make you more worldly.

really knows his stuff, yeah he is chill, he really likes to try to get us to understand. He can get so indulged with explaining everything that it can get boring, but its still good.Nothing you cant handle.
Really chill guy. Definitely knows his stuff and is able to see things from lots of different points of view. Class can be a little dull sometimes but it\'s not at all intolerable.
